Text: The Monica Seles of HouTownLiz I talked to Grant today and he told me you guys will be heading to Washington for Christmas and for your sisters wedding We wish it would have worked out for you to come to the big D but understand He also filled me on on your unstoppable ascendancy to the top of the charts of your clubs tennis elite Im not surprised and good luck Do you yell every time you hit the ball yet Well be working on a country weekend in January for us all to get together in the beautiful Hico Texas area As the realtors say it is the top of the hill country Martin
